OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be
OL,8,Fmainly dry but the odd shower possible
OL,9,Flater on.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FA mostly dry day with
OL,12,Fvariable amounts of cloud and some
OL,13,Fbright or sunny spells. Warm. The odd
OL,14,Fshower possible first thing, and again
OL,15,Fin the evening.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCloudy
OL,18,Fstart with the odd shower on Friday,
OL,19,Fthen dry and brighter by afternoon.
OL,20,FCloudy on Saturday with outbreaks of
OL,21,Frain. Mainly dry on Sunday.
